summary:
I retexture the old Vanila texture of the Slaughterfish
and make it much more Evil\\Dangerous texture...
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/k1rrwg.png[/IMG]
So like I saied in the small description... This mod
retexture the old Vanila version to a new cool
Evil\\Dangerous texture of the Slaughterfish!
I hope you guys will like it!

To install the mod i highly recommended to install
it with the Nexus Mod Manager.
